dct_description_sm: U.S. Coast Survey. A.D. Bache, Supt. ; triangulation by J.S. Williams, J.E. Hilgard and Lieut J.P. Roy Assts. ; hydrography by the parties under the command of Lt. Comdg. S.P. Lee and Comdr. W.T. Muse, U.S.N. Assistants.
Depths shown by shading and soundings.
Includes notes on sailing directions, soundings, and charts on light house and tides.
